<DATELINE>
   DUBAI
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Saudi Arabia's King Fahd has made two senior Moslem clerics cabinet
ministers and ordered the setting up of an Islamic guidance ministry, Reuter
reports from Dubai.
Sheikh Abdel Aziz Bin Abdullah Bin Baz, a member of the influential Higher
